             was indicted for <rs id="t18021027-36-off197" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18021027-36-off197" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18021027-36-off197" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18021027-36-cd198" type="crimeDate">6th of October</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18021027-36-off197 t18021027-36-cd198"></join>, a blanket, value 3s. 6d. two sheets, vlaue 6s. a pillow-case, value 1s. a bolster, value 3s. and a counterpane, value 5s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18021027-36-victim330" type="victimName">
                           Eleanor 
                           Roberts
                        <interp inst="t18021027-36-victim330" type="surname" value="Roberts"></interp>
